Let $z'$ be the complex number $z$ reflected across the line through 0 and $a + bi,$ and let $f(z)'$ be the complex number $f(z)$ reflected across the same line.  Then $|f(z)' - z'| = |f(z)|.$  Also, $|z - z'| = |f(z) - f(z)',$ so
\[|z - z'| = |(a + bi)z - (a - bi)z| = 2b |z|.\]Hence,
\[2b |z| = |f(z)| = |(a + bi)z| = |a + bi| |z| = 8 |z|,\]so $b = 4.$  Hence, $b^2 = \boxed{16}.$
